title: [Guardian Keep, Outer Wall]
description: The tall vine-covered stone wall to the south stretches to the east and west, providing a protected area for the tents and stands of various merchants.  A few brightly dressed elves can be heard haggling with a merchant over his assorted goods.

The tall shadowed stone wall to the south stretches to the east and west, providing a protected area for the tents and stands of various merchants.  A couple of hooded shapes can be seen moving quietly on various shopping errands.
